n <- length(df_new$price)
alpha <- 0.05

PreobrFisher <- function(r){
  Z <- FisherZ(r)
  SE_Z <- 1/sqrt(n-3)
  Z_alpha <- qnorm(1-alpha/2)
  
  Zmin <- Z - Z_alpha * SE_Z
  Zmax <- Z + Z_alpha * SE_Z
  
  rmin <- (exp(2*Zmin)-1)/(exp(2*Zmin)+1)
  rmax <- (exp(2*Zmax)-1)/(exp(2*Zmax)+1)
  
  interval <- c(rmin, rmax)
}
